    "I will not explore all ethical concerns but rather focus on three in particular.",
    "The frst ethical tension we face is related to the innumerable capabilities of the AI model.",
    "In moral philosophy, which deals with defning, suggesting, and evaluating the choices and actions that put individuals in a situation of well-being, it isn't easy to morally assess an artifact with an assortment of different scopes.",
    "Moreover, the capacities of a Large Language Model like GPT-3 are often defned but can multiply with its use.",
    "Given the breadth of possible uses in natural language, the model's capabilities can be infnite if not defned a priori and framed by its developers."
  ],
